'''荣威360'''是[[上汽集团|上汽集团]]旗下荣威子品牌的一款紧凑型轿车。

==概览==
荣威360于2015年推出，作为[[荣威350|荣威350]]紧凑型轿车的后续车型<ref>{{Cite web|title=上汽荣威360即将上市 价格将决定销路{{!}}界面新闻 · 快讯|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/345037.html|accessdate=2021-04-13|work=www.jiemian.com|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414083601/https://www.jiemian.com/article/345037.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
由于根据2014年初达成的协议，上汽可以使用[[通用汽车|通用汽车]]的发动机和变速箱，因此荣威360与上汽通用[[雪佛兰|雪佛兰]]、[[科鲁兹|科鲁兹]]共享相同的发动机和变速箱<ref>{{cite web|url=https://carnewschina.com/2015/08/19/this-is-the-new-roewe-360-for-the-chinese-car-market/|title=This is the new Roewe 360 for the Chinese car market|date=19 August 2015|website=Carnewschina.com|accessdate=14 November 2017|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128050701/https://carnewschina.com/2015/08/19/this-is-the-new-roewe-360-for-the-chinese-car-market/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=上汽荣威360：勇当中级车A咖|url=http://www.time-weekly.com/wap-article/31658|accessdate=2021-04-13|work=www.time-weekly.com|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413143120/http://www.time-weekly.com/wap-article/31658|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年底，360停产并以[[荣威i5|i5]]车型取代<ref>{{Cite web|title=i5接棒 荣威360停产_轿车市场|url=http://www.sohu.com/a/272193409_487651|accessdate=2021-04-13|work=www.sohu.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413234630/https://www.sohu.com/a/272193409_487651|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

